This git repository uses git submodules to build upon the 'minimal_surface'
repository and its code. This submodule contains a submodule itself, so
repeat recursively the following instructions. 
The contained submodules have to be initialized and updated manually. 
Hence use the following commands to use submodules correctly:

After cloning the superrepository initialize subrepositories with:
  -> git submodule init
  -> git submodule update

For updating subrepositories to the commit used in the superrepository use:
  -> git submodule update
